DISCIPLINARY CASES

01-2231. Cleveland Bar Assn. v. Harris.

On motion to supplement record. Motion granted. Record to be filed within ten days of the date of this entry.

Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., dissent.

On motion to seal supplemental record. Motion denied.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., dissent, would grant the motion to seal, but would make disclosure to the relator.
